            刚刚下地铁时是阴天，这不才半个多小时，竟然是蓝天白云，<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />&nbsp;正门前留下合影<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/26@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278447825" data-seq="278447826" data-pid="278447825" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6427">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278447825.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/48/wKgBEFpKFVmAOBnkAAWPnTmyeYo13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/48/wKgBEFpKFVmAOBnkAAWPnTmyeYo13.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278447825" alt="" />
