                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278509207">
            走进园子，大片的绿色让人心情顿时凉爽许多<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/23@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/23@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/23@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278447973" data-seq="278447974" data-pid="278447973" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6427">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278447973.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/4B/wKgBEFpKFV-AUjdMAAmG3lF8jVM86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/4B/wKgBEFpKFV-AUjdMAAmG3lF8jVM86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278447973" alt="" />
