                <a href="/poi/6427.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6427" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>圆明园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278749150">
            这里也曾是康熙61年，也就是1772年，皇四子胤祯请父皇来圆明圆“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64940.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="牡丹" target="_blank">牡丹</a>台”赏<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64940.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="牡丹" target="_blank">牡丹</a>，当时12岁的弘历第一次见到祖父，康熙见他特别聪明伶俐，就把这个皇孙直接带到身边，给他特殊的教育，以后乾隆登基后，就把“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64940.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="牡丹" target="_blank">牡丹</a>台”改为“镂月开云”，并且还建了“纪恩堂”，所以有三帝<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64940.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="牡丹" target="_blank">牡丹</a>台相见的故事，
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278447977" data-seq="278447978" data-pid="278447977" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6427">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278447977.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/4C/wKgBEFpKFWCAeygVAAZRCr81ngk42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/4C/wKgBEFpKFWCAeygVAAZRCr81ngk42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278447977" alt="" />
