            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278752409">
            从雍正到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64070.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="咸丰" target="_blank">咸丰</a>五代皇帝中，大部分都将每年三分之二的时间用来在此处理朝政，他们在园子里读书、观戏、赏景，这样的惬意生活是皇帝们处理繁杂事务后难得的放松心情的好去处！<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/6@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/6@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278448733" data-seq="278448734" data-pid="278448733" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278448733.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/B9/wKgBEFpKFeKAKColAAWvKlaW_0A93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/B9/wKgBEFpKFeKAKColAAWvKlaW_0A93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278448733" alt="" />
