            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278570055">
            这是当初<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63550.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海晏" target="_blank">海晏</a>堂前的水力钟喷泉⛲️，如今正中心的巨型贝壳番花的痕迹还有，但中间的涡轮喷水机以及周围的12个人身兽首早已不见踪影，想当初12个生肖按12个时辰轮流喷水🐳，正午时分同时喷水，周而复始，所以叫做水力钟喷泉，这可是欧式喷泉洋为中用，中西结合的一件杰作！<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/23@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278756772" data-seq="278756773" data-pid="278756772" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278756772.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:292px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/90/1E/wKgBEFpLgFSAdj8DAAFjvM_wE5822.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/90/1E/wKgBEFpLgFSAdj8DAAFjvM_wE5822.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278756772" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278754876">
            线法画，在线法<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12976.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="山东" target="_blank">山东</a>岸修建的7座对称的八字断墙，然后墙面挂上西方景物油画，远远看过去采用了透视原理展现了西方街市上的民俗生活，同时当时乾隆皇帝为了讨好香妃，还挂上了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13061.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="新疆" target="_blank">新疆</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/18008.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="阿克苏" target="_blank">阿克苏</a>地区街市上的风景画<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/29@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/29@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/29@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278450220" data-seq="278450221" data-pid="278450220" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6427">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278450220.html">
