                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278773417">
            这个万花阵可是当初用四尺多高的雕花砖墙模仿<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/14383.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="欧洲" target="_blank">欧洲</a>迷阵搭建而成，每到重要节日，皇帝坐在中心亭子内，让宫女、太监们手持黄绸带扎成的莲花灯，（所以也叫黄花阵）在阵势中来回穿梭，谁先到达谁就能得到皇帝的赐物，要知道，从入口到中心不到40米的距离，但由于无法找寻捷径，因此宫女、太监们要想得到赏赐可得费一番神，而皇帝早就看到他们乱窜的样子乐得哈哈大笑，哪里管得了作为玩物的宫女、太监们的心情？<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36@2x.png" style="width:28px;" /><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/36@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278449085" data-seq="278449086" data-pid="278449085" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="6427">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8173990/278449085.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/D3/wKgBEFpKFf-AemE3AAb9ktEkRVU60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D2/D3/wKgBEFpKFf-AemE3AAb9ktEkRVU60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278449085" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/6427.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="6427" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
